  {"word":"sophisticated","pos":"adj","ja":"高度な、洗練された","level":3,"cat":"general","ipa":"/səˈfɪstɪkeɪtɪd/","ex":"The new software uses a sophisticated algorithm to save time.","exJa":"その新しいソフトウェアは時間を節約する高度なアルゴリズムを使う。","collocations":["sophisticated technology","sophisticated taste"],"synonyms":["advanced","refined"],"distractorHint":["単純な","古風な","粗雑な"]},
  {"word":"spontaneous","pos":"adj","ja":"自発的な、即興の","level":3,"cat":"general","ipa":"/spɒnˈteɪniəs/","ex":"We took a spontaneous trip to the beach last weekend.","exJa":"私たちは先週末、思いつきで海辺へ旅行に行った。","collocations":["spontaneous decision","spontaneous reaction"],"synonyms":["impulsive","unplanned"],"distractorHint":["計画的な","強制された","遅延した"]},
  {"word":"sparse","pos":"adj","ja":"希薄な、まばらな","level":3,"cat":"general","ipa":"/spɑːrs/","ex":"The population in this region is very sparse.","exJa":"この地域の人口はとても希薄だ。","collocations":["sparse population","sparse information"],"synonyms":["scanty","thin"],"distractorHint":["密集した","豊富な","過剰な"]},
